{"tid":2352291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"房車撞單車漢不顧而去　女司機反問：「關我咩事？」","createTime":"2021-01-04T02:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T04:44:26.000Z","uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"969e702aea76fc20ff82bcfc89149d01f1647a14","tid":2352291,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:47:02.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一條車Cam短片，一輛房車在上水撞到一名單車漢，房車司機的冷血態度令網民極度不齒，短片迅即在多個社交平台上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmanhin.tsui.92%2Fvideos%2F243918753764349%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fmanhin.tsui.92%252Fvideos%252F243918753764349%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D476&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=e2cf4359\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmanhin.tsui.92%2Fvideos%2F243918753764349%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=476</a><br />\n<br />\n據了解，事發於昨晚(3日)7時許，一名姓黃(33歲)男子，踏乘單車至新運路及智昌路交界一燈位，並在行人過路處過路期間，一名姓楊(63歲)女子駕駛房車沿新運路駛至，猛撼過路單車漢。<br />\n根據車Cam影片，黃被撞至拋飛後，人仰車翻倒臥地上，惟楊女未有理會反而繼續加速離開。一名途經鐵騎士目擊意外發生，不值楊女所為，遂驅車緊追楊女，沿途多次響號及高叫「你仲走？你撞到人啊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOq6Mii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOq6Mii.jpg&h=ec2d5db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至約200米對開，鐵騎士終在上水火車站外截停涉事房車，並落車與楊女對質，期間楊理直氣壯，道：「關我咩事？佢(黃)衝紅燈喎！」鐵騎士即憤然指罵楊：「你咪走啊，你係咪傻咗？佢(黃)瞓咗喺度暈咗啊！」多名途人及駕駛者協助報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27mhSYq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27mhSYq.jpg&h=d5ce9e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至現場，將頭及腳重創的黃送院救治。警員向在場目擊者了解後，將楊女帶署調查，並拖走涉事房車檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBSg8wQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBSg8wQ.jpg&h=3a4c835d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據流傳車Cam片段，可見房車駛過新運路過路處時，交通燈顯示為綠燈，私家車可通行而行人則應在路旁等候轉燈，而踏乘單車人士在過路時亦應落車推車，惟有網友指摘楊女：「毫無悔意，單車係有錯，但係撞到人走咗去就係你(楊)唔啱。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGU3OwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGU3OwU.jpg&h=d921bda6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1062ad4094a88cf6348d80c665747293f9129771","tid":2352291,"uid":29130,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"今次我撐個C9呀<br />\n垃圾路權撚最好撞撚死哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a4e1c44079a1d1ed77ed07eb59584db462b1d0","tid":2352291,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1062ad4094a88cf6348d80c665747293f9129771","tid":2352291,"uid":29130,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"今次我撐個C9呀<br />\n垃圾路權撚最好撞撚死哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KU8Tru5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKU8Tru5.gif&h=79af1d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係條路到見到我就即刻撞過嚟<br />\n上網狗吠冇用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d143089796331845eba2448d016fc7aa614f546e","tid":2352291,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"衝紅燈單車狗俾人撞抵撚死啦"}]}